metadata.name: Complete SEL Setup
metadata.description:
Fully configured setup based on Tamtaro's recommended filters, sort orders, and Standard SEL described on the [github](https://github.com/Tam-Taro/SEL-Filtering-and-Sorting). Designed for those with debrid or usenet services, while seeking the highest quality results, minimal clutter, and complete coverage even when options are few. 

 * Comes with addons and formatter. Use my other templates to keep your existing addons/formatter. 
 * Standard SEL keeps around 20 results. Import Extended SEL Only template afterwards to keep 2x more. Github has more SEL options to try out. 
 * **â“˜ For catalogs, check out Github for AIOMetadata configs.**
 * Review the Language filter. Add your main languages to Preferred Languages, keep rest the same. 
 * Some addons are included but disabled; just turn them on if you use them (eg. Torbox). 
 * Comes with auto-synced urls for [Vidhin's Regexes](https://github.com/Vidhin05/Releases-Regex) to score & tag streams with my custom Formatter.
